// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0030 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 84e1ed40-27e2-5671-89ae-bc8f6eb10880

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.10*")
